The Core Idea
Read totalAttempts (the configured percentages) from the DB once ‚Äî that‚Äôs legitimate config. Never write back the attempts counter to the DB. Track it in a JVM-level ConcurrentHashMap keyed by sponsorId + supplierId. The DB row lock disappears entirely because there are zero UPDATE statements in the hot path.

